## About SPLICE

SPLICE (Splicegraph Probabilistic Learning for Isoform Change Estimation) is a comprehensive
differential splicing analysis tool developed by Mariano Aguilar Vela. The tool combines
annotation-free junction discovery, multi-way statistical testing, covariate regression,
heterogeneity detection, and functional annotation into a unified framework.

